reviewText: I bought this for my husband who loves this show.
Season 1 disc 1 doesnt work and cant be read.
This is the most entertaining tv show ever.  Blends light and dark comedy, subtle and knee-slapping jokes.  Love it.  DVD's work fine and are packaged well.

I'm unhappy with the quality of the copies. Maybe they tried to put too many shows on the DVDs but mine have audio dropouts galore. The speed of the copies is visibly faster than the air show was and it definitely doesn't add to the comedy.
What can I say.  You either love this show or hate it LOL.  The dvd's are great and they came very quickly.

If you have seen any episodes you know you get your money's worth with this show. My 18 year old and his best friend were so upset when Netflix pulled the show. They were so happy to get this for Christmas.
Gift, daughter &family loved it, as described, fast delivery
